    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，标题用'Hide today marker (Infra_LoadBalancer)'可以吗？还有时间格式，您希望用Z时区格式，然后坐标轴显示成日/月的样式？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "dateFormat",
        "axisFormat"
