    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Z格式和%d/%m都可以。那个5分钟的任务就叫'Today'吧，放在Section1里面，时间从08-08-09-01:00开始。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Today",
        "Section1",
